msgstr "Clave API"

#: includes/admin-settings.php:1208
msgid "Leave empty to keep the current key. In production define CHATBOT_GEMINI_API_KEY, CHATBOT_DEEPSEEK_API_KEY or CHATBOT_OPENAI_API_KEY in wp-config.php."
